| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1021 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f39c6e5-b8e7-597b-a1ff-170d3f46fdf0"
